      &lt;img alt="The Google search bar getting smashed by a gavel" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Uk8RbA0fIzYfo3nwiIjiWDKRnHY=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73505252/236780_Google_AntiTrust_Trial_Custom_Art_CVirginia__0002_2.0.png" /&gt;
