      &lt;img alt="Photo illustration of a gavel casting a shadow over the Google logo" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RYKfdHEEcVT8ZiKqQQPUEw1xZlc=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73505170/236780_Google_AntiTrust_Trial_Custom_Art_CVirginia__0000_4.0.png" /&gt;
